1 Weiler Data Explorations

DAPI <- datRaw[, grep("DAPI*", colnames(datRaw), value = TRUE), with = FALSE]
pca <- prcomp(as.matrix(DAPI), center = TRUE, scale = FALSE)
pcax <- pca$x
pc1 <- pcax[,1]
pc1 <- pc1 - min(pc1)
plot(pc1, pch = 16, cex = .25, col = alpha("red", 0.25))

getElbows(pca$sdev)
